headline.main: THE JOHN BROWN INVASION.; Official History of the Whole Affair.

docs.lead_paragraph: MESSAGE OF GOV. WISE TO THE LEGISLATURE OF VIRGINIA. To the Senate and House of Delegates of the General Assembly of the Common wealth of Virginia: GENTLEMEN : Up to a late period I had fondly hoped to close my official term and part from my Executive labors with naught but cause of congratulation on the condition of Commonwealth.
